name: unlocked (tuslir)
description:
you hate the place you're in, but where else could be better?
say goodbye to your loved ones and go north.

_________

school project i made back in december 2021.

design and code by me.

________

how to play: run in browser. pick a level to play. use mouse to move and interact with objects. when a level is finished, click button to return to main menu.

the canvas/UI is a little bit weird, this is a known issue.

________

assets used: industrial platformer tilesheet by KanCade / 1-bit icons part 1 and part 2 by VectorPixel / lo-fi music pack by VOiD1 Gaming / m3x6 font by Daniel Linssen / dialog boxes + more for gb studio by Wyatt199x

thank you!
